A IRC bot that queries lilurl to shorten URLs.

Usage: ./lilbot.rb -l <lilhostname> [-b <botname>] [-i <irchost>
                     [-p <ircport>[-c <channel> -k <channelkey>]]] 
 --lilhost, -l <s>:   Hostname of lilurl server
 --botname, -b <s>:   Nick of the bot (default: lilbot)
 --irchost, -i <s>:   IRC host to connect to (default: irc.cat.pdx.edu)
 --ircport, -p <i>:   Port to connect to (default: 6697)
 --channel, -c <s>:   Default channel to join. Do NOT include the leading "#"
     --key, -k <s>:   Optional key for the default channel

Only works on SSL ports.
